{"tid":1996169,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Naughty Dog 副總裁霸氣回應 The Last of Us 2 劇透事件：厭惡同性戀就給我他X的滾開","createTime":"2020-04-30T19:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T05:56:51.000Z","uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d43b2e0e8d7b450f0745bee426cbd6b5c91adb5c","tid":1996169,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:28:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/ALIEN/2020-4/Image%20184.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FALIEN%2F2020-4%2FImage%2520184.png&h=6c59e2f5&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n由 Sony 本家開發的《最後生還者 Part II》（The Last of Us Part II）》終於決定要在 6 月 19 日發售。但開發商頑皮狗副總裁確在 IG 直接開嗆玩家「不爽不要買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」。<br />\n<br />\n事情的起因是日前《最後生還者 Part II》許多內容包含劇情影片在網路上遭人爆料。雖然頑皮狗一天後就在官方推特呼籲玩家不要觀看洩漏或爆雷，不過仍然檔不住一些好奇心滿滿的玩家。<br />\n<br />\n但主要問題不是在於這些人物設定，問題就在於看過的玩家很多人對於二代的劇情本身並不滿意，也因此有玩家開始遷怒於頑皮狗是為了滿足自己的「政治正確」而編寫了這樣的劇情（但究竟是不是就只有頑皮狗自己知道）。<br />\n<br />\n在玩家開始砲轟遊戲，甚至到處散播拒買言論後，大概把頑皮狗逼急了，副總裁 Neil Druckmann在 IG 發了限時動態，引述了美國歌手 Kurt Cobain 過去曾說過的話：<br />\n<br />\n「我想告訴我們的粉絲，如果你們當中有人厭惡同性戀、不同膚色或女性，請幫我們一個忙－給我他X的滾開，不用參加我們的演出，也不用來買我們的唱片。（當然這裡指的是遊戲）」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/ALIEN/2020-4/t1bpq6bn0sv41.jpg?versionId=zFEnmXD4Gjqpfk8C90HKSmp41q9SM_he\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FALIEN%2F2020-4%2Ft1bpq6bn0sv41.jpg%3FversionId%3DzFEnmXD4Gjqpfk8C90HKSmp41q9SM_he&h=f74e2e17&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n先不管究竟是不是「政治正確」，不論什麼理由，在這節骨眼上開嗆玩家絕對不智。這對於《最後生還者 Part 2》的銷量最後究竟會不會有影響，等到發售當日就會知道了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/42955/neil-druckmann-said-on-instagram-dont-buy-our-game\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F42955%2Fneil-druckmann-said-on-instagram-dont-buy-our-game&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rJS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=e1f39a5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/42955/neil-druckmann-said-on-instagram-dont-buy-our-game</a>"},{"pid":"45224dd2e3aec54d0d8072ae012a7897d65dee72","tid":1996169,"uid":48858,"like":2,"dislike":23,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:35:09.000Z","msg":"Xboxone Contana 留名系統啟動，<br />\n請勿負評干擾運作。"},{"pid":"10fb8bfd45c249db06f3453a973549da955773fc","tid":1996169,"uid":15948,"like":37,"dislike":6,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:37:20.000Z","msg":"好 就唔撚買！<br />\n最憎gay閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c614d97f886a12f0ab076ad2086747551857c28d","tid":1996169,"uid":100772,"like":3,"dislike":30,"score":-27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:38:28.000Z","msg":"睇達哥玩咪得 洗咩買"},{"pid":"cc72e2aecc551efcac7ac5589711649b31f58df3","tid":1996169,"uid":37666,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:38:34.000Z","msg":"唔關女權事<br />\n係個劇情ON9呀屌<br />\n上一集要我保護個細路女<br />\n今集要我殺死佢???"},{"pid":"fd0b8facbeb558b80f2d03b2b1d83c449b081639","tid":1996169,"uid":85586,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:38:53.000Z","msg":"battlefied 5 2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a20093d810b454ee45a9af17b29537135867a2","tid":1996169,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c614d97f886a12f0ab076ad2086747551857c28d","tid":1996169,"uid":100772,"like":3,"dislike":30,"score":-27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:38:28.000Z","msg":"睇達哥玩咪得 洗咩買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:41:39.000Z","msg":"x2"},{"pid":"21c299417962fc54eaa42d96886a45d612179226","tid":1996169,"uid":268053,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"cc72e2aecc551e